![Episode13.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1575063287545-7EQ4M2RPB2D0UL314BWQ/Episode13.jpg)

Forget Oscar night, these are the awards you have been waiting for! On this episode the guys give out awards to the best comic book media from last year, including Best Movie of 2017, Beest TV Show, Coolest Moment and more! All the winners were chosen by YOU the fans who used Facebook to vote for your favorites! Check out all the winners chosen by the greatest fans on the planet and join us every week for a BRAND NEW EPISODE!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

